**For large σ (σ > 5):****p\_i ≈ 2 × exp(-σ\_i²/2) / (σ\_i √(2π))**

**Even simpler approximation:****p\_i ≈ 10^{-σ\_i²/2 × log₁₀(e)}****p\_i ≈ 10^{-0.217 σ\_i²}**

